00:16:09,540 --> 00:16:10,500
¡Señor Grimmer!

192
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,640
Hola, doctor.

193
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,420
Pensaba que no iba a llegar nunca.

194
00:16:16,820 --> 00:16:18,500
Por favor, échale una mano.

195
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:23,340
Ese chico es buena persona.

196
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,460
